sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User as User
  participant App as Mobile App
  participant Store as Workspace Store
  participant Repo as Repo Service
  participant Net as Remote Origin
  participant Resolver as Language Resolver
  participant Editor as CodeMirror View
  participant Prefs as Settings

  User->>App: Launch app
  App->>Store: loadRecentWorkspaces()
  Store-->>App: workspace summaries
  App-->>User: Render workspace list

  User->>App: Tap workspace title
  App->>Prefs: readTitleAffordanceMode()
  Prefs-->>App: mobile accent enabled
  App-->>User: Show subtle underline on phone

  App->>Store: openWorkspace(workspaceId)
  Store-->>App: repo path + cached tree version
  App->>Repo: hydrate(repoPath)
  Repo-->>App: metadata and branch

  alt wifi and stale repo
    App->>Repo: scheduleBackgroundPull()
    Repo->>Net: git fetch --prune
    Net-->>Repo: refs and pack data
    Repo->>Net: git pull --ff-only
    Net-->>Repo: updated branch head
    Repo-->>App: tree invalidated
    App->>Store: saveLastSyncAt()
  else offline or manual mode
    Repo-->>App: keep cached snapshot
  end

  App-->>User: Render tree and header
  User->>App: Open src/utils/string.ts
  App->>Repo: readFile(blobId)
  Repo-->>App: utf8 content
  App->>Resolver: resolveByExtension("ts")
  Resolver-->>App: typescript mode + fold support
  App->>Editor: createView(doc, extensions)
  Editor-->>User: highlighted source with folding

  User->>App: Open Sample_typescript_ets.ets
  App->>Repo: readFile(blobId)
  Repo-->>App: utf8 content
  App->>Resolver: resolveByExtension("ets")
  Resolver-->>App: alias to typescript
  App->>Editor: updateLanguage(typescript)
  Editor-->>User: highlighted alias sample

  User->>App: Open a legacy language sample
  App->>Resolver: resolveByExtension("jinja")
  Resolver-->>App: legacy mode without fold service
  App->>Editor: hideFoldGutter()
  Editor-->>User: full-width code without empty gutter

  opt file is unsupported
    App->>Resolver: resolveByExtension("unknown")
    Resolver-->>App: no exact match
    App->>Editor: keep plain text mode
    App-->>User: show lightweight unsupported notice
  end

  User->>App: Return to workspace list
  App->>Store: saveLastOpenedFile()
  Store-->>App: ok
  App-->>User: preserve scroll position

  Note over App,Editor: The viewer should favor believable fixture data because manual QA decisions are based on what reviewers actually read.

  User->>App: Trigger screenshot capture
  App->>Editor: waitForLayoutStable()
  Editor-->>App: stable
  App-->>User: capture ready

  User->>App: Open release notes from docs
  App->>Repo: readFile(readmeBlobId)
  Repo-->>App: markdown text
  App->>Resolver: resolveByExtension("md")
  Resolver-->>App: markdown mode
  App->>Editor: swapDocument(markdownDoc)
  Editor-->>User: rendered markdown source preview

  Note over Store,Prefs: Workspace metadata and UI preferences should survive app restarts.